cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use this methodology, please cite it as below."
title: "DIVE-PL: A reproducible AI tool-chain methodology for building survey research studies"
abstract: "An end-to-end, reproducible framework that integrates an LLM design/orchestration agent, an independent LLM reviewer (LLM-as-judge), REDCap electronic data capture, and AI-built analytics dashboards, wrapped in an open-science layer (Zenodo, OSF, GitHub Pages). Demonstrated on a cross-sectional online survey of recreational divers in Poland."
